<h3>Getting Started</h3>
<p>SocialChess is a multiplayer chess app currently in <strong>early development</strong>. All you need to play is a modern web browser and you're all set!</p>
<% if signed_in? %>
<%= link_to "Play Now", play_path, :class => "button orange" %>
<% else %>
<%= link_to "Sign Up", signup_path, :class => "button orange" %>
